<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239553>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 15. Male genitalia. 12 — Calochromus harauensis sp. nov.; 13 — C. lamellatus; 14 — C. kelantanensis sp. nov.; 15 — C. impressicornis. Scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239553/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239552>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 11. General appearance. 1 — Calochromus lamellatus; 2 — C. impressicornis; 3 — C. kelantanensis sp. nov.; 4 — C. harauensis sp. nov. Head. 5 — C. kelantanensis sp. nov.; 6 — C. harauensis sp. nov. Antenna. 7 — C. harauensis sp. nov.; 8 — C. lamellatus. Pronotum, the holotype of: 9 — Plateros brevicornis; 10 — P. melancholicus; 11 — P. barronensis. Photographs 9 – 11 taken by P. Hudson. Scales 2.0 mm (Figs 1 – 4), 1.0 mm (Figs 5 – 8)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239552/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

